90</a></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><guid ispermalink="false">发布：39139570</guid><pubDate> Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:00:00 -0400</pubDate><dc:creator>张涛</dc:creator><dc:creator>张喜龙</dc:creator><dc:creator>陈建全</dc:creator><dc:creator>张修伟</dc:creator><dc:creator>张云雷</dc:creator><dc:date>2024-08-14</dc:date><dc:source>免疫学前沿</dc:source><dc:title>利用微生物抗原作为癌症抗原：癌症免疫治疗的一个有前途的途径</dc:title><dc:identifier>下午：39139570</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> PMC：PMC11319170</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> doi:10.3389/fimmu.2024.1411490</dc:identifier></item></channel></rss>